{"id":"obeisance","term":"Obeisance","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Homage or reverence to any one (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 37:7\">Gen. 37:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 43:28\">43:28</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 37:7","Genesis 43:28"]}